<help skills scribe>

This skill, learned by some magic users, allows them to
concentrate some of their power in a scroll that can later be
called forth.  Often it is less powerful than their original
spell, but then again, it takes little effort to use it. 

Syntax:  scribe [spell]
<color=red>
See Also:  concoct, construct
</color>
Notes:  You must have a writing utensil and blank scroll of
	appropriate quality in order to scribe a spell.
</help>
